    "• Flask: A Python framework [37] designed for crafting web applications.",
    "Flask equips developers with essential tools for managing HTTP requests, routing, HTML templates, and user sessions.",
    "• Critique: Developed by Inspired Cognition [38], Critique is a cutting-edge quality monitoring Python library tailored for generative AI.",
    "It simplifies the detection of potential faults by computing scores from a set of metrics to evaluate the quality of text generated by LLMs.In conjunction with these Python libraries, Dialogflow [39], a Google-developed platform for creating Chatbots and conversational agents, was integrated.",
    "Additionally, Ngrok,foot_2 a web application development tool, was employed to create secure tunnels between local servers and the external world, facilitating testing and sharing of applications."
